  "prompt": "Why am I blocked from asking questions under anonymous basis on Quora?",
  "response": "I'm sorry to hear you're having trouble asking questions anonymously on Quora. There could be several reasons why you're experiencing this issue:\n\n1. **Policy Violations**: If you've previously posted questions or content that violated Quora's [Content Policies](https://www.quora.com/about/content-policies), such as harassment, spam, or inappropriate material, Quora may restrict certain features on your account, including the ability to ask questions anonymously.\n\n2. **Usage Limits**: To prevent abuse, Quora may impose limits on the number of anonymous questions you can post within a specific timeframe. If you've reached this limit, you might be temporarily blocked from asking more anonymously.\n\n3. **Account Restrictions**: If your account is under review or has been restricted for any reason, certain functionalities, including anonymity options, might be disabled.\n\n4. **Technical Issues**: Sometimes, technical glitches or bugs can temporarily prevent certain features from working correctly. Clearing your browser cache, trying a different browser, or updating the Quora app (if you're using one) might help resolve these issues.\n\n5. **Verification Requirements**: In some cases, Quora may require additional verification for certain actions to ensure the authenticity of users and content. Ensure that your account is fully verified and up-to-date.\n\n**Steps You Can Take:**\n\n- **Review Quora's Policies**: Make sure you're familiar with [Quora's Community Policies](https://www.quora.com/about/content-policies) to ensure your content aligns with their guidelines.\n\n- **Check Notifications or Emails**: Look for any messages from Quora that might explain the restriction. Quora often notifies users about policy violations or account issues via email or notifications within the platform.\n\n- **Contact Quora Support**: If you're unsure why you're blocked or believe it might be a mistake, reach out to [Quora's Help Center](https://www.quora.com/contact) for personalized assistance. Provide them with relevant details about your issue to help them address it effectively.\n\n- **Wait It Out**: If the block is temporary, it might lift after a certain period. In the meantime, ensure that any new content you post adheres to Quora's guidelines to avoid further restrictions.\n\nRemember to always engage respectfully and responsibly on platforms like Quora to maintain a positive experience for yourself and the community.",
